<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>STUDY THE SCRIPTURES</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathienni sikul kai hitiu,
 Micheng cheng a ding ahi;
 A lien, a neu kaikhawm hitiu,
 A mei-apa ding ahi.

[V2]
 Hung kai un, a pha ie!
 I gamah zung tha hen la;
 A thu chuh a pha ie!
 I nam hun hihhawih in a.

[V3]
 2. Bible simin a ngaihtuoh ui,
 Pathien leh mihing thu lul;
 Thu baihlam I het phak a um,
 A thuk le Pathien lungthim.

[V4]
 3. Krista chanchin pha deih umte,
 Hukdamna lampi ei hilh;
 Damsung tawihdan hawih ei sinsak,
 Thih muon theihna thu ei hilh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>426</hymn_number>
</song>